OL,6,FThe Speaker of the House of Commons
OL,7,Fconfirmed MPs will sit on Saturday
OL,8,Ffrom 11am to "take forward legislative
OL,9,Fproposals to ensure the continued
OL,10,Foperation of British Steel blast
OL,11,Ffurnaces is safeguarded".
OL,13,FMPs left Parliament to go back to
OL,14,Ftheir constituencies this week, as the
OL,15,FHouse of Commons rose for Easter
OL,16,Frecess on Tuesday.
OL,18,FRecalling Parliament is rare, and was
OL,19,Flast done in 2021 over Afghanistan.
OL,20,FThere have only been 34 recalls since
OL,21,F1948.
