OL,6,FThe Chinese owner of British Steel,
OL,7,FJingye, claims the plant's two blast
OL,8,Ffurnaces are "no longer financially
OL,9,Fsustainable" and the raw materials
OL,10,Fneeded to keep them operational are
OL,11,Frunning out, prompting fears they
OL,12,Fcould imminently be switched off.
