OL,6,FIt said the business is running at a
OL,7,Floss of #700,000 a day maintaining the
OL,8,Fplant. Jingye had already rejected a
OL,9,F#500 million state rescue package to
OL,10,Fhelp the business transition towards
OL,11,Fgreener steel production.
OL,13,FThe Scunthorpe steelworks employs
OL,14,F2,700 people.
