OL,6,FITV News understands many MPs are
OL,7,Fconfused about the extent of the
OL,8,Frecall, and whether or not they will
OL,9,Fobliged to return. A number of Labour
OL,10,FMPs are understood to be heading off
OL,11,Fon holiday, with some boarding flights
OL,12,Fas the recall announcement was made.
OL,14,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer had said
OL,15,Fon Thursday that "all options are on
OL,16,Fthe table" for the plant.
